text: All statistical analyses were performed using GraphPad 6.0 software (GraphPad Software, Inc. La Jolla, CA, USA), and data were presented as means Â± standard error of mean (SEM) or as a percentage. For the analysis of the significance of differences, we used one-way analysis of variance (ANOVA) or two-tailed Student's t-test. P values equal to or less than 0.05 were considered statistically significant.
